<text id="02-output-contract" title="AI Leverage Estimation Model Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="850" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema draft-07 for a leverage-adjusted estimate. Validator rejects estimates without per-leaf classes, evidence rows, or band-versioning.</summary>

  <section title="Schema (JSON Schema draft-07)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/ai-leverage-estimate.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["engagement_id", "band_version", "tasks", "totals"],
  "properties": {
    "engagement_id": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
    "band_version": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^[0-9]{4}-Q[1-4]$"},
    "tasks": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["leaf_id", "task_class", "raw_hours", "multiplier_band", "evidence_rows", "adjusted_hours"],
        "properties": {
          "leaf_id": {"type": "string"},
          "task_class": {"enum": ["glue", "scaffold", "tests", "business-logic", "regulated", "novel"]},
          "raw_hours": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0.25},
          "multiplier_band": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["low", "mid", "high"],
            "properties": {
              "low": {"type": "number", "minimum": 1.0, "maximum": 8.0},
              "mid": {"type": "number", "minimum": 1.0, "maximum": 8.0},
              "high": {"type": "number", "minimum": 1.0, "maximum": 8.0}
            }
          },
          "evidence_rows": {
            "type": "array",
            "minItems": 1,
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "required": ["log_task_id", "date", "planned_hours", "actual_hours"],
              "properties": {
                "log_task_id": {"type": "string"},
                "date": {"type": "string", "format": "date"},
                "planned_hours": {"type": "number"},
                "actual_hours": {"type": "number"}
              }
            }
          },
          "adjusted_hours": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["low", "mid", "high"],
            "properties": {
              "low": {"type": "number"},
              "mid": {"type": "number"},
              "high": {"type": "number"}
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "totals": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["mid_hours", "low_hours", "high_hours"],
      "properties": {
        "mid_hours": {"type": "number"},
        "low_hours": {"type": "number"},
        "high_hours": {"type": "number"}
      }
    },
    "fallback_reason": {"type": "string", "description": "non-empty iff skip-this-methodology rule fired"}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "engagement_id": "acme-checkout-2026-Q2",
  "band_version": "2026-Q2",
  "tasks": [
    {
      "leaf_id": "wbs-3.1-stripe-webhook-handler",
      "task_class": "glue",
      "raw_hours": 6.0,
      "multiplier_band": {"low": 2.0, "mid": 3.0, "high": 4.0},
      "evidence_rows": [
        {"log_task_id": "task-1023", "date": "2026-03-14", "planned_hours": 8, "actual_hours": 2.5},
        {"log_task_id": "task-1041", "date": "2026-04-02", "planned_hours": 6, "actual_hours": 2.0}
      ],
      "adjusted_hours": {"low": 3.0, "mid": 2.0, "high": 1.5}
    }
  ],
  "totals": {"mid_hours": 2.0, "low_hours": 1.5, "high_hours": 3.0}
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "engagement_id": "x",
  "band_version": "Q2-2026",
  "tasks": [
    {"leaf_id": "wbs-1", "task_class": "fast", "raw_hours": 8, "multiplier_band": {"mid": 5.0}}
  ]
}
]]></code>
    <note>band_version pattern wrong; task_class not in enum; multiplier_band missing low/high; evidence_rows absent; adjusted_hours absent; totals missing.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>multiplier_band.mid &gt; 5.0 — exceeds observed throughput; reject as vanity.</item>
      <item>evidence_rows empty — every band must cite measured throughput rows.</item>
      <item>band_version older than current quarter — bands rot; refuse.</item>
      <item>task_class = "novel" with multiplier_band.mid &gt; 1.2 — novel domain has no AI track record.</item>
      <item>fallback_reason set AND tasks non-empty — skip path is exclusive.</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-ai-leverage-estimation-model.py">Validator script enforcing this schema</reference>
</text>
